summary: Changes the music in the main menu to the FREE hardstyle release of Headhunterz from 2012 - Dragonborn.
descriptionHtml:
Changes the music in the main menu to the FREE hardstyle release of Headhunterz in 2012 - Dragonborn. Intro and outro were cut because they were not lore-friendly enough.
The quality was reduced as well. Check out the original in full quality here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VaiHTvifGt0

I know there was already a mod created similar to this but I'm actually learning to mod skyrim and wanted to share my own version.
I do not claim to have created the track used, it was made by the music producer Headhunterz/Willem Rebergen as a FREE release.
All credit for the track goes to him. Please check out his website: https://www.headhunterz.com/

Big thanks to arecaidianfox for his wav to xwm converter. You can find it here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32075/?

No copyright infrengement intended! Contact me personally if You are against an upload which You may have rights to, instead of contacting Nexusmods.com about a copyright infringement. I will instantly take down the upload. Thank You.
author: Finnickk
